            <thetext>The user agent string of Opera 10 is currently parsed as:

fullversion = &quot;10..00&quot;

As Opera today also integrates the presto version string into the browser, we should maybe use the presto version instead of the opera version e.g. &quot;2.2.0&quot; instead of &quot;10.0&quot; as we do for gecko and webkit as well.</thetext>
